msgstr "Because it’s a work in progress, this site has a long way to go before replacing weather.gov. In the meantime, you can still <a href='https://www.weather.gov' class='usa-link'>access weather.gov</a> and all the tools it offers. You should continue to rely on weather.gov as the authoritative source for weather information."

